Package com.github.fge.largetext.sequence Description

Subsequences of a LargeText

This package deals with calls to LargeText.charAt(int) and LargeText.subSequence(int, int). The goal is to create a sequence with the minimal set of TextRanges enclosing the required index or indices.

This can either be a single range SingleTextRangeCharSequence or more than one range (MultiTextRangeCharSequence), or even the empty sequence EmptyCharSequence).

The CharSequenceFactory class is in charge of generating such ranges; in turn, it is used by sequences generated by this package to, again, obtain subsequences.
